Hellpeon looked around at the surrounding shield and laughed as a ield of 
Chaochitan energy surrounded him which would protect him for the most part of 
the shields enclosing around him to try and suish him. The beast then hovered 
into the hole it made and began to fly throughout the ship as it sent eight 
huge beams of chaochitan energy all around.
